You have any kids?

377
00:31:16,068 --> 00:31:19,040
你为什么这么问?
Why are you asking me if I have children?

378
00:31:19,040 --> 00:31:21,008
我很好奇
I'm curious.

379
00:31:21,008 --> 00:31:24,060
我没有  你有么?
I do not. Do you have children?

380
00:31:24,060 --> 00:31:26,023
没有
No.

