I was there a minute.

397
00:32:55,078 --> 00:32:59,037
那个孩子从前门出来了
Then this kid comes right through the front door.

398
00:32:59,037 --> 00:33:02,010
我叫他把手举起来
I tell him to put his hands up.

399
00:33:02,010 --> 00:33:05,045
